---
title: Teriyaki Beef Rice Bowl with sesame veg and umami aioli
description: Fragrant ginger-infused rice adorned with a sprinkling of chives sits alongside tangy, umami beef mince and vibrant green veg in this quick, straightforward and delicious dish.
